data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained brick townhome, nestled in the serene suburb of Towson. This delightful property boasts 3 cozy bedrooms and 2 full modern bathrooms, complemented by the convenience of off-street parking.  As you step inside, you're greeted by a recently updated kitchen that epitomizes contemporary elegance. The open-concept design seamlessly blends the living and dining areas, creating a perfect space for entertaining and daily living. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring lustrous granite countertops, high-quality stainless steel appliances, a practical kitchen island, and new, stylish cabinetry that offers ample storage.  Adjacent to the kitchen, the home opens to a covered patio, providing a tranquil outdoor retreat for relaxation or hosting gatherings. The fenced-in rear yard adds a layer of privacy and security, making it an ideal space for pets or outdoor activities.  A notable feature of this townhome is its new roof, ensuring durability and peace of mind for years to come. The current owner's love and care for the property are evident throughout, with thoughtful maintenance and updates that add to the home's appeal.  Location-wise, this townhome is a gem. It's situated conveniently close to a plethora of shopping options and a diverse range of restaurants, catering to all your lifestyle needs. Additionally, the proximity to I-695 offers easy access for commuting and exploring the greater Baltimore area.  This Towson townhome is more than just a house; it's a warm and inviting home waiting for its next chapter with you. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.
